<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Artist Profile Claim Update</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; }
      .header { background-color: #fff7e6; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffa500; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
      h2 { color: #ff8c00; margin: 0; }
      a { color: #ff8c00; text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Artist Profile Claim Update</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{artist_name}},</p>

        <p>{{message}}</p>

        <p>Our team will review your profile claim request, which typically takes up to 3 business days to process. We'll keep you updated throughout the entire process and notify you once your claim has been approved.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance during this process, feel free to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:{{support_email}}">{{support_email}}</a>.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br/>The Looop Music Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Looop Music. Please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
